A mysterious fire outbreak has razed a section of Ogbette main market Enugu in the afternoon. The fire, which destroyed shops and goods in some sections of the market, forced traders to scamper for safety and left affected traders stranded and confused. As at the time of filling this report, the cause of fire was yet to be ascertained .
It was gathered if not the Swift intervention of fire fighters in Enugu, the fire would have razed the entire market. It was gathered that the area mostly affected was the the foam section near the old part. The Chief Fire Officer of Enugu, Okwudiri Oha said they were able to extinguish the fire early. 